==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪə(r)|-eɪə(r)]]

===Adjective===
'''player'''
#of something that "[[play]]s" itself; a [[player piano]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#One who plays, or amuses themself; one without serious aims; an idler; a trifler.
#One who plays any game.
#A dramatic [[actor]].
#One who plays on a [[musical instrument]].
#A [[gamester]]; a [[gambler]].
#A person who [[play the field|plays the field]] rather than having a long-term sexual relationship.

